name: 219 on the Ocean with Private Bath
neighborhood_overview: Quiet, residential neighborhood within a 7 minute walk to the T.
description:
An old Boston home in Savin Hill. My place is close to The T, overlooks Malibu and Savin Hill Beaches, easy to get here from the airport, and easy to get downtown. We are close to restaurants, the JFK Museum, and the Harbor-walk. You’ll love my place because of the quiet and beauty. You will have your solitude and privacy. My place is good for solo adventurers, business travelers, medical people. All walks of life welcomed here. Registered with the City of Boston #STR383505

The space
Private full bath connected to the private room.

Other things to note
The bed is a double, or Full size bed, not a Queen. it is 54 x 75 inches
